
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "FAQ";
}
<main class="mt-5 pt-4" style="height:60vh;">
<div class="container wow fadeIn">
        <div class="container mb-5">
            <div id="faqAccordion">
                <div class="card mb-2">
                    <div class="card-header" id="heading1">
                        <h2 class="mb-0">
                            <button class="btn btn-link collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse1">
                                如何創建帳戶？
                            </button>
                        </h2>
                    </div>
                    <div id="collapse1" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="heading1" data-parent="#faqAccordion">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <p>創建帳戶非常簡單。點擊網頁右上角的"註冊"按鈕，填寫必要的個人信息，然後點擊"創建帳戶"即可。</p>
                            <p class="text-muted mt-2">
                                <small>發布日期: 2023/01/15</small>
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card mb-2">
                    <div class="card-header" id="heading2">
                        <h2 class="mb-0">
                            <button class="btn btn-link collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse2" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse2">
                                如何重置密碼？
                            </button>
                        </h2>
                    </div>
                    <div id="collapse2" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="heading2" data-parent="#faqAccordion">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <p>如果您忘記了密碼，請點擊登錄頁面上的"忘記密碼"鏈接。輸入您的電子郵件地址，我們將向您發送重置密碼的說明。</p>
                            <p class="text-muted mt-2">
                                <small>發布日期: 2023/02/20</small>
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card mb-2">
                    <div class="card-header" id="heading3">
                        <h2 class="mb-0">
                            <button class="btn btn-link collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse3" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse3">
                                如何聯繫客戶支持？
                            </button>
                        </h2>
                    </div>
                    <div id="collapse3" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="heading3" data-parent="#faqAccordion">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <p>您可以通過以下方式聯繫我們的客戶支持團隊：</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>發送電子郵件至 support@example.com</li>
                                <li>撥打我們的客服熱線 0800-123-456</li>
                                <li>使用網站底部的在線聊天功能</li>
                            </ul>
                            <p class="text-muted mt-2">
                                <small>發布日期: 2023/03/10</small>
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</main>

@section Style
{
    <style>
        .faq-header {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 2rem 0;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        .card-header .btn-link {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .card-header .btn-link:hover,
        .card-header .btn-link:focus {
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .card-header .btn-link:not(.collapsed) {
            color: #0056b3;
        }
    </style>
}
